      <text>Digestive beta-glucosidases from the wood-feeding higher termite, Nasutitermes takasagoensis: intestinal distribution, molecular characterization, and alteration in sites of expression.</text>
      <annotation id="17">
        <infon key="type">Gene</infon>
        <infon key="identifier"></infon>
